|'''1947'''
|*''Die Farshvundene Velt: Idishe shtet, Idishe mentshn.'' 
''*The Vanished World: Jewish Cities, Jewish People''
|Edited by [[Rafeal Abramovitch]]; title, text and captions in [[English language|English]] and [[Yiddish]]; includes photographs by R. Vishniac, A. Kacyzna, M. Kipnis and others. First edition of the earliest and most comprehensive graphic pictorial history of Jewish life at the beginning of the Nazi era.
